data.description: This beautiful move in ready home is located within the Trilogy community of Wickenburg Ranch in the HONCHO subdivision with breath taking views! This meticulously cared for home offers beautiful grey cabinetry in the kitchen with granite counter tops and a kitchen island.  The open concept design opens to the dining/living room. A wired speaker system enhances your living experience. You have a generous owner's suite that offers stunning views of Lake Park.  The en-suite offers double sinks, a walk in shower and a generous walk in closet.  The split floor plan offers a guest room with it's own exterior door leading to a private sitting area.  This home also offers a leased SOLAR system $109.15 monthly.  Nothing left to do but bring your bags!!  The amenities leave nothing to be desired!
